      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEMORIES (6) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around Sandown in 29.51 to score two back then following on with a 29.61 win over 515m at Sandown. Expected to push the clock again here. PAW NIMBUS (2) produced a moderate run last time when sixth at The Meadows over 525m behind Paw Waverly (30.54) in a Free For All. Was a winner the start prior. The form out of last race has been strong. Worth another chance. BISCOTTINO (3) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by a neck (25.28) at Shepparton. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. CANYA SPEED (4) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts ago but finished fifth last time (25.76) at Murray Bridge.",
